<plot>This is a promotional short film for _The Great Waltz (1972)_ (qv), a biography of the great Viennese composer 'Johann Strauß' (qv). The director and two costars express their appreciation to the Austrian government for allowing to make the film in the actual locations where Strauß lived and where his music was performed.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?517784</url></doc>
